      <title>Android Sending an SMS to multiple recipients sends as an MMS</title>
      <link>https://mikedixson.com/sending-an-sms-to-multiple-recipients-sends-as-an-mms/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Jan 2013 12:34:43 +0000</pubDate>
